data.description: The open living great room, kitchen and dining area of this home makes a great place to welcome guests. 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and indoor laundry round out the comfortable living space. Corner lot in a newer neighborhood in East Bakersfield. Fresh paint and window blinds throughout the house. Close to Hart Park, Lake Ming, and the Kern River Canyon for outdoor adventures. Easy access to both crosstown freeways, Highways 58 and 178, to quickly get  downtown. Owned solar with substantial extra capacity for future EV charging, pool/spa, etc.
